	<h1 class="title">《分手大师》堪称排片大师，拿下 1.5 亿首周末票房</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/73/small/73.jpg?1415670876" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">俞斯译</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-06-30 16:30:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/1304/medium/1304.jpg?1436640144" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


